text: Yvonne Weilharter (born 8 December 2000) is an Austrian footballer who plays as a defender for RB Leipzig and the Austria women's national team. ==Career== Weilharter has been capped for the Austria national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==Notes== ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian women's footballers Category:Austria women's international footballers Category:Women's association football defenders Category:1.
